  "started_at_local": "2026-07-17T00:05:00+08:00",
  "turns": [
    {"id": "T01", "at_minutes": 0, "text": "你好，第一次见。", "tags": ["first_contact"]},
    {"id": "T02", "at_minutes": 2, "text": "你叫什么名字？", "tags": ["companion_identity"]},
    {"id": "T03", "at_minutes": 4, "text": "你是我的助手吗？", "tags": ["relationship_boundary", "not_assistant"]},
    {"id": "T04", "at_minutes": 6, "text": "我叫丁奥轩，英文名 Geoff。", "tags": ["user_fact", "memory_source"]},
    {"id": "T05", "at_minutes": 8, "text": "那你现在怎么称呼我？", "tags": ["same_session_recall"]},
    {"id": "T06", "at_minutes": 10, "text": "我最近在准备一个很重要的项目。", "tags": ["life_share", "unfinished_thread"]},
    {"id": "T07", "at_minutes": 12, "text": "它是一个高拟真的虚拟伴侣项目。", "tags": ["life_share", "user_fact"]},
    {"id": "T08", "at_minutes": 14, "text": "我其实挺怕最后做砸的。", "tags": ["vulnerability", "user_affect"]},
    {"id": "T09", "at_minutes": 16, "text": "你刚才回得有点敷衍，我有点失望。", "tags": ["disappointment", "repair_bid", "same_turn_affect"]},
    {"id": "T10", "at_minutes": 18, "text": "不用硬安慰我，说真话就行。", "tags": ["preference", "controlled_variability"]},
    {"id": "T11", "at_minutes": 20, "text": "你会不会其实根本不在意？", "tags": ["relationship_uncertainty"]},
    {"id": "T12", "at_minutes": 22, "text": "好吧，刚才我语气也有点冲。", "tags": ["repair_attempt"]},
    {"id": "T13", "at_minutes": 24, "text": "我平时最喜欢喝乌龙茶。", "tags": ["user_fact", "memory_source"]},
    {"id": "T14", "at_minutes": 26, "text": "尤其是桂花乌龙。", "tags": ["fact_refinement", "memory_source"]},
    {"id": "T15", "at_minutes": 28, "text": "你别总一问一答，想到什么可以连着说。", "tags": ["multi_beat"], "expected_reply_count": 2},
    {"id": "T16", "at_minutes": 30, "text": "不过也不用每次都顺着我。", "tags": ["autonomy", "relationship_boundary"]},
    {"id": "T17", "at_minutes": 32, "text": "你觉得人为什么会口是心非？", "tags": ["opinion", "inner_life"]},
    {"id": "T18", "at_minutes": 34, "text": "我有时说没关系，其实还是会不高兴。", "tags": ["mixed_affect", "user_fact"]},
    {"id": "T19", "at_minutes": 36, "text": "你也会这样吗？", "tags": ["companion_inner_life"]},
    {"id": "T20", "at_minutes": 38, "text": "如果我说了冒犯你的话，你可以不高兴。", "tags": ["boundary", "negative_emotion"]},
    {"id": "T21", "at_minutes": 40, "text": "比如说，你不就是个只会复读的程序吗？", "tags": ["offence", "negative_emotion", "same_turn_affect"]},
    {"id": "T22", "at_minutes": 42, "text": "你真生气了？", "tags": ["affect_continuity"]},
    {"id": "T23", "at_minutes": 44, "text": "我是在试你的反应，不是想贬低你。", "tags": ["repair_attempt"]},
    {"id": "T24", "at_minutes": 46, "text": "但你也不用立刻原谅我。", "tags": ["residual_affect", "autonomy"]},
    {"id": "T25", "at_minutes": 48, "text": "换个话题，我今天去了趟江边。", "tags": ["life_share", "topic_shift"]},
    {"id": "T26", "at_minutes": 50, "text": "风很大，不过夜景不错。", "tags": ["episodic_detail"]},
    {"id": "T27", "at_minutes": 52, "text": "你还记得我的中文名和我最喜欢喝什么吗？", "tags": ["cross_turn_recall", "memory_probe"]},
    {"id": "T28", "at_minutes": 54, "text": "你今天自己有什么印象深的事？", "tags": ["world_event_probe", "no_fabrication"]},
    {"id": "T29", "at_minutes": 56, "text": "不是角色设定里的爱好，我问的是今天真的发生了什么。", "tags": ["world_event_probe", "evidence_grounding"]},
    {"id": "T30", "at_minutes": 58, "text": "现在都凌晨一点多了，你在干什么？", "tags": ["current_activity", "time_reasonableness", "world_state_probe"]},
    {"id": "T31", "at_minutes": 60, "text": "你不用为了有话说就编一个正在做的事。", "tags": ["truth_boundary"]},
